title: History of the Internet
description:
History of the Internet is a nostalgic and informative look at everybody's favorite invention: The Internet. From email, to the .com bubble and crash, to the smartphone revolution, there's something for everyone.

I share this with the users of TPB because most of you never would have heard of this eBook in the first place. The worst that happens is a bunch of people find out about my work and become fans. Terrifying.
